      <title>贸易商衡量股市的下一步行动保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/traders-gauging-stock-market-s-next-move-keep-wary-eye-on-flows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周将S＆amp; P 500指数置于更正的抛售以其相对平静而闻名。现在，随着投资者对市场情绪的搜索指标和恢复或进一步幻灯片提示的关键价格水平，他们还需要观看更模糊的方面：市场流动性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/traders-gauging-stock-market-s-next-move-keep-wary-eye-on-flows</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
